data.text:
Hi Louise,

A descendant of Joseph Gilbert of Russell Co., VA has had a DNA match with a descendant of Benjamin Gilbert of Maryland.This could be a very big hint as to the roots of the Russell Co. Gilbert line.Information on this Benjamin can be found here:

http://www.janegilbert.org/gilbertdna/ydnakits/benjaminofmd.htmhttp://www.janegilbert.org/gilbertdna/ydnakits/benjaminofmd.htm

And the lineage of the Joseph Gilbert descendant here:

http://www.janegilbert.org/gilbertdna/ydnakits/josofrusselva.htmhttp://www.janegilbert.org/gilbertdna/ydnakits/josofrusselva.htm

Jane
